		<title>SWISSto12 Raises $70 Million in Series C Round To Scale Multi-Orbit Business</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/swissto12-raises-70-million-series-c-multi-orbit-satellite/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ekemini]]></dc:creator>
